Here's the corrected PlantUML sequence diagram for IBM Cognos Analytics to visualize business data:

```plantuml
@startuml IBM_cognos-analytics-to-visualize-business-data

actor User
participant "Node.js Scripts" as NodeJS
participant "IBM Db2 Warehouse" as Db2
participant "Netezza Performance Server" as Netezza
participant "IBM Cognos Analytics" as Cognos

User -> NodeJS: Execute generate-product-business-data.js
NodeJS -> NodeJS: Generate sample data (stores, products, sales)
alt Using Db2 Warehouse
    NodeJS -> Db2: Create tables
    NodeJS -> Db2: Insert data
else Using Netezza
    NodeJS -> Netezza: Create tables
    NodeJS -> Netezza: Insert data
end

User -> Cognos: Connect to data warehouse
alt Connected to Db2
    Cognos -> Db2: Establish connection
else Connected to Netezza
    Cognos -> Netezza: Establish connection
end

User -> Cognos: Create data modules
Cognos -> Db2: Query data schema
Db2 --> Cognos: Return schema
Cognos -> Cognos: Build data model

User -> Cognos: Build dashboards
Cognos -> Db2: Query data for visualization
Db2 --> Cognos: Return results
Cognos -> User: Display dashboards

@enduml
```